  • Constructor Details

    • Sites

      public Sites​(java.lang.String name, int mortgageValue, int index, java.lang.String colour, int[] rentValues, int houseCost)
      This Constructs a Site with specified name, mortgage value, board index, colour, rent values and house cost.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the site.
      mortgageValue - The mortgage value of the site. Site cost is double this value.
      index - The board index of the site.
      colour - The colour of the site.
      rentValues - An array containing the rent prices for each site.
      houseCost - The cost of building a house on this site. Hotel cost is the same.

      public void buySite​(Player player, int cost)

      Parameters:

    • colourGroupCheck

      public void colourGroupCheck()
      Used to check if a newly bought site completes a colour set of sites. If so Increase rent of all sites and set boolean fullSet to true.
